data.description: 3 bedroom home with nearly 4.5 fenced acres, pond, stable, and a detached 1200 sq.ft. garage/workshop just minutes from downtown Punta Gorda. A great property for a horse enthusiast or one who is desiring a large workshop area for hobbies, storage, wood-working, etc. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has a front, east facing 350 sq.ft. lanai area, an attached 1 vehicle carport, and a 12x23 utility/craft/storage room. The large detached garage space is 40'x30', has one overhead garage door, over 30 feet of storage cabinetry and counter-top work space, and an exhaust fan unit. This building is ideal for wood-working, painting, collector car restoration, etc. The house and garage are set well back from the road with the pasture area occupying the front of the property, affording privacy, peace, and quiet! Brokered And Advertised By: COLDWELL BANKER MORRIS REALTY, Listing Agent: JAMES THIEL
